                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-212-off1077 t18300916-212-crimeloc1080"></join>. I saw the prisoner take this gown from the door on the 31st of August - she rolled it up, and put it under her shawl; I went and pushed her further into the shop - she dropped it from under her shawl, and pretended to ask the price of it; it had been hanging on two nails - she took it off one and then off the other, and pretended to be looking at a spencer.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-212-person1754">
                  JAMES 
                  GUY
